  • Class
    Description
    Add
    The Add class implements the Command interface and is responsible for adding a SpaceMarine object to a collection.
    Clear
    Command to clear the collection managed by the CollectionManager.
    Command
    The Command interface defines the structure for command classes in the application.
    ExecuteScript
    The ExecuteScript class implements the Command interface and is responsible for executing a script file that contains a series of commands.
    Exit
    Command to terminate the program.
    FilterStartsWithAchievements
    Command to filter SpaceMarine objects based on whether their achievements start with a specified substring.
    Help
    Command to provide a list of available commands along with their descriptions.
    Load
    Command to load a collection from a file.
    MinByMeleeWeapon
    Command to find the SpaceMarine object with the minimum melee weapon value.
    PrintUniqueLoyal
    Command to print SpaceMarine objects with unique loyalty values.
    RemoveByID
    Command to remove a SpaceMarine object from the collection by its ID.
    RemoveGreater
    Command to remove all SpaceMarine objects from the collection that are greater than a specified object.
    RemoveLower
    Command to remove all SpaceMarine objects from the collection that are lower than a specified object.
    Save
    Command to save the collection of SpaceMarine objects to a file.
    Show
    Command to display all SpaceMarine objects in the collection.
    Sort
    Command to sort SpaceMarine objects in the collection.
    UpdateId
    Command to update a SpaceMarine object in the collection based on its ID.
